Standard Chartered Saadiq Seeks Expansion Into Nigeria, Tanzania

-- B y   D a n a   E l   B a l t a j i
-- 
2011-04-04T14:36:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/standard-chartered-saadiq-seeks-expansion-into-nigeria-tanzania.html
Standard Chartered Plc (STAN) ’s Islamic
unit is “exploring opportunities” for expansion into Nigeria,
Tanzania and  Kenya , according to the Dubai-based Chief Executive
Officer of Standard Chartered Saadiq.  “We would like to have a presence in countries with
significant Muslim populations,” Afaq Khan said in a telephone
interview today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
